M_WIP_Application\\Data\\SqlHelper.cs:line 85\r\n   at MTM_WIP_Application.Data.InventoryDao.ExecuteNonQueryAsync(String sql, Dictionary`2 parameters, Boolean useAsync) in C:\\Users\\johnk\\source\\repos\\MTM_WIP_Application\\Data\\InventoryDao.cs:line 36', '', 'HandleInventoryExceptionAsync', '', 'JOHNSPC', 'Microsoft Windows NT 10.0.26100.0', '4.6.0.0+9fab027866eac3963d08f5d29c75fd555494438a', '2025-06-01 23:52:38');
